('dee8a273-0833-5511-866a-40135dfc88ed', '1edff391-2539-4f62-a859-502cc0d1935e', 'Due to the effects of global warming, the ice in ___ is shrinking, which endangers many species of polar animals.', '由於全球暖化的影響，___ 的冰正在縮減，這危害了許多極地動物的生存。', 'the Arctic Ocean', 'the Amazon River', 'the Sahara Desert', 'the Rocky Mountains', 'Arctic 來自於希臘語 arktos，意為「熊」，這與北極熊（polar bear）有關。', 'Arctic (北極的) → 聯想 Arctic Bear (北極熊) 生活在極寒的北極。', '2026-07-10 02:19:36', '2026-07-10 02:19:36'),
